openinfra_core 1.4.2 API

Packages 
Package Description
de.btu.openinfra.backend
This package contains the OpenInfRA main application class (Webbrowser: http://localhost:8080/openinfra_backend/rest/v1/projects).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db
This package contains database related stuff which is required to bootstrap the database connections.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.converter
This package contains PostgreSQL specific data converter to support proper interaction between the database layer and the database.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos
This package implements all DAO classes which are used to access the JPA persistence layer (database).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.file
This package contains the DAO classes of the file service.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.meta
This package implements all DAO classes which are used to access the JPA persistence layer (database).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.rbac
This package contains DAO classes for role-based access control (rbac).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.webapp
This package contains the DAO classes of the web-application schema.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.jpa.model
Auto generated and minor documented classes referring to subject databases: project and mostly system.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.jpa.model.file
This package contains the model classes of the file service.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.jpa.model.meta
Auto generated and minor documented classes referring to meta data.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.jpa.model.rbac
This package contains model classes for role-based access control (rbac).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.jpa.model.webapp
This package holds model classes of the web-application schema.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos
Currently undocumented classes representing plain old java objects (POJO) instantiated by DAO classes and mostly consumed by rest resources.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.file
This package contains POJOs of the file service.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.meta  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.project  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.rbac
This package contains POJO classes for role-based access control (rbac).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.solr
This package contains POJO classes for the Solr search.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.webapp
This package contains POJO classes of the web-application schema.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac
This package contains classes of the role-based access control system (RBAC).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac.file
This package contains the classes for securing the file service.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac.meta
This package contains classes for role-based access control concerning meta data.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac.rbac
This package contains classes to secure access to role-based access control.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.exception
This package contains classes for exception handling.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.filter
This package is used to hold ContainerRequestFilter or ContainerResponseFilter classes.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.helper
This package contains different helper classes used by the JSP-based GUI elements and to provide images of the CISAR projects.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest
This package provides classes used to produce the JSON and XML outputs for RESTful services related to both projects and system database schemas.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.csv  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.file
This package contains rest resources for the file service.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.meta
Domain classes used to produce the JSON and XML output for the RESTful services related to the meta database schema.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.pdf
This package contains REST resources for PDF transformation.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.project
This package contains REST resources which exclusively refer to the project databases.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.rbac
This package contains REST interfaces for role-based access control (rbac).
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.solr
This package contains REST resources for the Solr search.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.system
This package contains REST resources which exclusively refer to the system database.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view
This package contains the view components in order to provide a graphical user interface.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view.file  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view.project  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view.solr  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.view.system  
de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.webapp
This package contains the REST resources of the web-application schema.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.servlet
This package contains OpenInfRA servlets.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.solr
This package contains all main classes for the interaction with Solr.
de.btu.openinfra.backend.solr.enums
This package contains all enumerations that are used in OpenInfRA.
